{"tid":2058533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【健康碼】港商：兩地不互認新冠病毒檢測結果 豁免安排作用不大","createTime":"2020-06-10T08:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T08:48:16.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6e147bc1c13b24da49aeebffba67f5448e6b822","tid":2058533,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:43:02.000Z","msg":"【健康碼】港商：兩地不互認新冠病毒檢測結果 豁免安排作用不大<br />\n6小時前<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府正研究跟內地互認「健康碼」，有在內地設廠的港商希望盡快落實，又指政府早前推出的豁免檢疫安排，由於兩地不能互認檢測結果，對他們幫助不大。<br />\n<br />\n梁偉浩的鐘表公司在東莞設廠，他跟另外六名香港員工疫情爆發以來，大部分時間都被困東莞。<br />\n<br />\n梁偉浩申請了政府豁免部分港商返港的十四日檢疫，但無用過，他稱問題出於內地政府不承認香港的核酸檢測結果，返內地時都要隔離十四日。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=393902&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393902%26hot%3D1&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVaxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=fc5fb953\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393902%26hot%3D1&h=2f9df7e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=393902&amp;hot=1</a>"},{"pid":"070e0d848bf593579e6923c228d0100b86bfc417","tid":2058533,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}